He won't feel a thing.
<SYNC Start=5430876><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5457334><P Class=ENCC>
You're awake.
<SYNC Start=5458667><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5462251><P Class=ENCC>
Is it your birthday today?
<SYNC Start=5464376><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5466626><P Class=ENCC>
My birthday is a few days away
<SYNC Start=5468376><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5469084><P Class=ENCC>
