<SYNC Start=5476501><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5477209><P Class=ENCC>
not just you.
<SYNC Start=5479334><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5479501><P Class=ENCC>
If you still want someone to love you only,<br>
heaven is not the right place for you.
<SYNC Start=5482742><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5504792><P Class=ENCC>
You must think that I'm cheap.
<SYNC Start=5506501><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5507876><P Class=ENCC>
No.
<SYNC Start=5509084><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5510167><P Class=ENCC>
Everyone will get their favorites
<SYNC Start=5512459><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5512584><P Class=ENCC>
with no regret.
<SYNC Start=5513833><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5513834><P Class=ENCC>
But you'd make the wrong choice.
<SYNC Start=5515542><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5516209><P Class=ENCC>
It is judge by me.
<SYNC Start=5517917><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5518209><P Class=ENCC>
This will be a secret<br>
if we agreed not to disclosure
<SYNC Start=5522626><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5528626><P Class=ENCC>
I need to ask my wife
<SYNC Start=5530542><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5533834><P Class=ENCC>
I feel pity for you
<SYNC Start=5534708><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5534709><P Class=ENCC>
