bury you with sorrow.
<SYNC Start=5536469><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5539459><P Class=ENCC>
Let's change the subject.
<SYNC Start=5541167><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5545876><P Class=ENCC>
Let's talk about your future
<SYNC Start=5548209><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5548376><P Class=ENCC>
and your dreams?
<SYNC Start=5551084><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5552251><P Class=ENCC>
I don't have a future
<SYNC Start=5553917><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5554792><P Class=ENCC>
I've been living a nightmare for years
<SYNC Start=5559209><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5562001><P Class=ENCC>
I remember the day you stabbed me.
<SYNC Start=5564209><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5565001><P Class=ENCC>
Lying on the floor, I heard<br>
