<SYNC Start=5568126><P Class=ENCC>
I was so moved.
<SYNC Start=5569459><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5570542><P Class=ENCC>
That night
<SYNC Start=5571626><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5572834><P Class=ENCC>
I had my only sweet dream.
<SYNC Start=5575834><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5576542><P Class=ENCC>
You whispered in my ear
<SYNC Start=5578876><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
