<SYNC Start=5739834><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5740709><P Class=ENCC>
I just want to ask you one thing.
<SYNC Start=5742417><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5743126><P Class=ENCC>
If we had no son
<SYNC Start=5744251><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5744792><P Class=ENCC>
