<SYNC Start=5746042><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5792501><P Class=ENCC>
It won't open!
<SYNC Start=5793917><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5837417><P Class=ENCC>
You haven't answered my question yet.
<SYNC Start=5840376><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5844792><P Class=ENCC>
Yuyan
<SYNC Start=5845709><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5846084><P Class=ENCC>
