<SYNC Start=5872959><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5873126><P Class=ENCC>
You're really 3 moves<br>
ahead of everyone.
<SYNC Start=5874959><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5875584><P Class=ENCC>
It's all part of the<br>
"switch operation" plan.
<SYNC Start=5879834><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5880584><P Class=ENCC>
Quick, check the painting.
<SYNC Start=5882084><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5882167><P Class=ENCC>
Give me some time.
<SYNC Start=5883334><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5896626><P Class=ENCC>
Be happy together.
<SYNC Start=5898334><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5928209><P Class=ENCC>
Move even a few steps from me
<SYNC Start=5930000><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5930001><P Class=ENCC>
and the alarm sounds.
<SYNC Start=5931542><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5931792><P Class=ENCC>
You're not going anywhere
<SYNC Start=5933417><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5936126><P Class=ENCC>
without my permission.
<SYNC Start=5937751><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5956959><P Class=ENCC>
Where is Xiao Jinhan?
<SYNC Start=5958084><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5962501><P Class=ENCC>
He must have gone to<br>
Yamamoto to get the scroll.
<SYNC Start=5964667><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5967709><P Class=ENCC>
