<SYNC Start=5969292><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5972334><P Class=ENCC>
Only you can save him now.
<SYNC Start=5973959><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5975167><P Class=ENCC>
Why should I?
<SYNC Start=5976751><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5977834><P Class=ENCC>
Because you love him
<SYNC Start=5979251><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5983167><P Class=ENCC>
I'll go with you.
<SYNC Start=5984542><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5985917><P Class=ENCC>
