<SYNC Start=5987626><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5988584><P Class=ENCC>
If I die
<SYNC Start=5990001><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5991042><P Class=ENCC>
I give him to you.
<SYNC Start=5992542><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5996542><P Class=ENCC>
If I die
<SYNC Start=5998001><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5998792><P Class=ENCC>
I don't even have the right<br>
