<SYNC Start=6134084><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=6135792><P Class=ENCC>
You can never possess
<SYNC Start=6137709><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=6138292><P Class=ENCC>
